      <title>南苏丹总统呼吁保持冷静以应对军队紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/south-sudan-president-calls-for-calm-amid-rumors-of-army-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南苏丹总统萨尔瓦·基尔呼吁民众保持冷静，因为有传言称数名高级军事官员被解职可能会引发这个冲突频发国家的暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/south-sudan-president-calls-for-calm-amid-rumors-of-army-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 16:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普大选前夕，加拿大外商投资趋于稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/foreign-investment-into-canada-steadied-ahead-of-trump-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第三季度，加拿大的外国直接投资保持稳定，这是一个令人鼓舞的迹象，表明尽管美国大选前的不确定性加剧，但企业仍继续将资本留在这个北方国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/foreign-investment-into-canada-steadied-ahead-of-trump-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 16:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴尼耶让步 勒庞提出更多预算要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/le-pen-s-party-makes-more-budget-demands-as-barnier-gives-ground</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 做出重要让步放弃提高电力税的计划后，玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 领导的国民联盟进一步要求修改法国政府 2025 年预算法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/le-pen-s-party-makes-more-budget-demands-as-barnier-gives-ground</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 15:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谢恩鲍姆称比亚迪墨西哥工厂计划尚未“确定”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/sheinbaum-says-that-byd-s-plan-for-mexico-plant-isn-t-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆周四表示，墨西哥尚未收到中国汽车公司在墨西哥建立工厂的“明确”项目提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/sheinbaum-says-that-byd-s-plan-for-mexico-plant-isn-t-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 15:50:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚将重新计票，TikTok 被指偏袒候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/romania-says-it-was-a-target-of-cyberattack-in-presidential-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚最高法院下令重新计票，因为一位鲜为人知的极端民族主义候选人在周日的总统选举中意外获胜，而安全小组表示，此次竞选受到了旨在影响选举结果的网络行动的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/romania-says-it-was-a-target-of-cyberattack-in-presidential-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 15:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格鲁吉亚执政党将欧盟入盟谈判推迟至 2028 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/georgian-ruling-party-delays-eu-membership-talks-until-2028</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚政府表示，四年内不会参加加入欧盟的谈判，此举加深了人们对这个黑海国家未来道路的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/georgian-ruling-party-delays-eu-membership-talks-until-2028</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 15:15:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法雷奥因欧洲竞争力“大幅”下降而裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/valeo-to-cut-jobs-on-massive-loss-of-european-competitiveness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法雷奥公司 (Valeo SA) 计划在欧洲裁员约 1,000 人，并关闭位于法国的两家工厂，原因是汽车行业前景黯淡，而且面对廉价的中国产品，该地区的竞争力下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/valeo-to-cut-jobs-on-massive-loss-of-european-competitiveness</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 15:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管土耳其有否决权，塞浦路斯仍考虑加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/cyprus-considers-nato-application-despite-certain-turkish-veto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞浦路斯总统尼科斯·赫里斯托杜利迪斯周四表示，塞浦路斯希望为成为北约成员国做好准备，尽管土耳其誓言将否决此举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/cyprus-considers-nato-application-despite-certain-turkish-veto</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 14:52:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢布暴跌迫使俄罗斯央行进一步加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/ruble-s-plunge-pressures-bank-of-russia-for-steeper-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近期卢布大幅贬值，加大了俄罗斯央行上调基准利率的压力，其利率可能创下乌克兰战争爆发以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/ruble-s-plunge-pressures-bank-of-russia-for-steeper-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 12:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
